    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>to a bowl, cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> and set aside</p><p>Peel and finely grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
