    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated garlic </strong>to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!) with your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>ground coriander</strong></p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
