    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomato</strong> to a separate bowl with the <strong>quick-pickled pink onion</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion salad</strong></p>",
